Alternate Data Systems

- Microsoft NTFS Substructure.
- You can use the same attributes for many alternate streams.

Can be used for
- Store other files (images, virus and etc)
- Modify stream metadata
- DoS

Interesting behaviors
- ADS filesize is not included in default filesize
- Does not change the checksum
- ADS is lost with Zip, Rar, ARJ, Base64, FAT32

Usage
- notepad 
	> host_filename:stream
- type
	>  input_file > host_filename:stream
